00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:29.610
for-profit education
corporations of today.

00:10:29.620 --> 00:10:33.190
But this big business approach
to education hasn't come without

00:10:33.190 --> 00:10:34.616
controversy.

00:10:34.630 --> 00:10:37.930
With so much money on the line many
turn to the schools that show the best

00:10:37.930 --> 00:10:41.860
numbers, the best chances at a new
job when you graduate. But can you

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:44.492
